## Proposed Changes

### Dashboard — Startup Hardening

#### [MODIFY] [firebase_options.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/dashboard/lib/firebase_options.dart)
Add an assertion after the `web` constant: in debug mode throw `AssertionError('FIREBASE_WEB_API_KEY is empty …')` when `apiKey`, `appId`, or `messagingSenderId` are empty strings.

#### [MODIFY] [main.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/dashboard/lib/main.dart)
Add `/` route → `GoRouter` `redirect` that maps `/` to `/login`. Change `initialLocation` to `/` so that a blank navigation to the app always resolves to `/login` instead of a 404 white screen.

---

### Dashboard — Command Center UI

#### [MODIFY] [live_feed_tile.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/dashboard/lib/features/command/widgets/live_feed_tile.dart)
Replace the `ColoredBox` placeholder with a `VideoPlayer` widget initialised from `streamUrl`. When `streamUrl` is absent, show a styled placeholder card instead of a black box. Remove the mis-used `Expanded` inside a non-`Flex` `Column` (current compile warning).

#### [NEW] [transcript_panel.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/dashboard/lib/features/command/widgets/transcript_panel.dart)
`StreamBuilder` on Firestore `incidents/{incidentId}/transcript` ordered by timestamp. Renders lines in a auto-scrolling `ListView`.

#### [NEW] [action_controls.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/dashboard/lib/features/command/widgets/action_controls.dart)
Three `FilledButton.tonal` buttons: **ACKNOWLEDGE**, **LOG ACTION**, **RESOLVE**. Each calls the matching method on `incidentListProvider`'s notifier (to be added) writing the action to RTDB `live_incidents/{hotelId}/{incidentId}`.

#### [MODIFY] [command_center_screen.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/dashboard/lib/features/command/screens/command_center_screen.dart)
Restructure right column into three vertical sections:
1. [LiveFeedTile](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/dashboard/lib/features/command/widgets/live_feed_tile.dart#4-25) (top, flex 2)
2. `TranscriptPanel` (middle, flex 2)
3. `ActionControls` + `ResponderLog` (bottom, flex 1)

