### Dashboard — Incident Detail Page

#### [MODIFY] [incident_detail_screen.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/dashboard/lib/features/command/screens/incident_detail_screen.dart)
Replace stub with a `StreamBuilder` on Firestore `incidents/{incidentId}`. Displays: incident ID, status badge, severity chip, room/floor/wing, guest name, AI summary, hazard tag, timestamps.

