### Mobile — Splash Auth-Check

#### [MODIFY] [router.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/mobile/lib/core/router.dart)
Convert [SplashScreen](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/mobile/lib/core/router.dart#53-64) to `ConsumerStatefulWidget`. Watch `authStateProvider` and `guestProfileProvider`. On first frame:
- If `authState` is loading → stay on splash.
- If `authState` is null (not signed in) → `context.go('/checkin')`.
- If `authState` is non-null AND `guestProfileProvider` is non-null → `context.go('/home')`.
- If `authState` is non-null but profile is null → `context.go('/checkin')` (profile setup pending).

---

### Mobile — SOSHomeScreen Language Selector

#### [MODIFY] [sos_home_screen.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/mobile/lib/features/sos/screens/sos_home_screen.dart)
Replace `Text('Language: $language')` with a `DropdownButton<String>` listing `['en', 'hi', 'ar', 'fr', 'es']`. On change, call `ref.read(guestProfileProvider.notifier).setProfile(profile.copyWith(language: newValue))`. Add `copyWith` to [GuestProfile](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/mobile/lib/features/auth/providers/auth_provider.dart#4-19).

