### Mobile — Audio Capture

#### [MODIFY] [camera_service.dart](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/mobile/lib/services/camera_service.dart)
Implement [captureAudio()](file:///d:/gdgsolutions/mobile/lib/services/camera_service.dart#29-32):
```dart
Future<String> captureAudio() async {
  if (_controller == null || !_controller!.value.isInitialized) {
    await initialize();
  }
  await _controller!.startAudioOnlyRecording();
  await Future.delayed(const Duration(seconds: 2));
  final file = await _controller!.stopAudioOnlyRecording();
  final bytes = await file.readAsBytes();
  return base64Encode(bytes);
}
```

